---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import portadaImg from '../assets/img/portada.avif';
---
<!-- BEGIN: HeroSection -->
        <!-- BEGIN: HeroSection -->
        <section class="relative w-full min-h-screen bg-dark-theme flex flex-col" data-purpose="hero-section">
            <!-- Background Image (Background on mobile, right side on desktop) -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full lg:left-auto lg:w-1/2 z-0">
                <Image alt="Lujo Terraza al atardecer" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src={portadaImg} loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />

                <!-- Dark overlay for readability on mobile only -->
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 lg:hidden"></div>

                <!-- Info Box -->
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-8 right-6 lg:bottom-12 lg:right-12 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-md text-white p-4 max-w-[240px] rounded-lg border border-white/10 text-xs z-20">
                    <p>Más del 60% de las terrazas planas en áreas urbanas están funcionalmente desaprovechadas o sin
                        uso.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Text Content -->
            <div
                class="relative z-10 w-full mt-20 flex-grow flex flex-col justify-center px-6 lg:px-16 pt-12 pb-12 lg:py-32 text-white lg:w-1/2">
                <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-7xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight mb-8 max-w-xl">
                    Transformamos Espacios en Oasis Urbanos
                </h1>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mt-16 text-base lg:text-lg mb-10 max-w-md">
                    Transformamos terrazas vacías en espacios recreativos de alta calidad, combinando diseño, tecnología
                    y materiales premium.
                </p>
                <div>
                    <a class="relative mt-16 inline-flex items-center gap-4 bg-[#222222] border border-gray-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-medium overflow-hidden group transition-all duration-300"
                        href="https://wa.me/5491159516786?text=Hola,%20quisiera%20cotizar%20un%20proyecto"
                        target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        <!-- Círculo que se expande -->
                        <span
                            class="absolute right-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-6 h-6 bg-white rounded-full transition-transform duration-500 ease-out group-hover:scale-[30] z-0 origin-center"></span>

                        <!-- Texto -->
                        <span
                            class="relative z-10 text-white group-hover:text-black transition-colors duration-300 font-semibold">
                            Cotizar sin costo
                        </span>

                        <!-- Icono -->
                        <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 text-black">
                            <svg class="transition-transform duration-500 -rotate-45 group-hover:rotate-0" fill="none"
                                height="16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
                                <path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- END: HeroSection -->